OL,3,CHusband's 'life ruined' after wife and
OL,4,Cson killed on way back from birthday
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FIn a statement read out at Derby Crown
OL,8,FCourt as Hill was sentenced on Friday,
OL,9,FMr Boyack, who was married for 35
OL,10,Fyears, said the lives of him and his
OL,11,Fson were "ruined".
OL,13,FProsecutor Laura Pitman told the court
OL,14,Fhow Hill had been driving at speeds of
OL,15,Fup to 72mph on a 50mph stretch of road
OL,16,Fin wet weather and that the anti-lock
OL,17,Fbraking systems on his BMW was faulty,
OL,18,Fwhich may have lessened the speed at
OL,19,Fthe point of impact had it been
OL,20,Fworking correctly.
