OL,7,FHe had been seen carrying out
OL,8,F"aggressive" overtakes ahead of the
OL,9,Fcrash, with one driver reporting
OL,10,FHill's passenger had rolled down the
OL,11,Fwindow, laughed and put his middle
OL,12,Ffinger up as they sped past him.
OL,14,FMs Pitman said the route the Boyacks
OL,15,Fwould have taken on their journey
OL,16,Fhome, up the A1M, was blocked due to a
OL,17,Fcrash, so they took an alternative
OL,18,Froute home on the A632 through
OL,19,FChesterfield instead.
