OL,7,FShe told the court how William and
OL,8,FAlex saw Stephen's Hyundai "jump in
OL,9,Fthe air" and roll onto a grass verge
OL,10,Fafter the crash, with dashcam footage
OL,11,Ffrom their vehicle showing them both
OL,12,Frunning towards the car to try and get
OL,13,Fthem out of it.
OL,15,FMr Boyack ran back to his car to try
OL,16,Fand find a fire extinguisher and
OL,17,Fsomething he could smash the window
OL,18,Fwith, returning with a claw hammer,
OL,19,Fand "knew his wife was dead" as soon
OL,20,Fas he saw her.
