OL,7,FMs Pitman said: "While this was going
OL,8,Fon, William saw Mr Hill and his
OL,9,Fpassenger watching but offered no help.
OL,11,F"In temper he approached them and
OL,12,Fasked them if they were in BMW, but he
OL,13,Fdidn't get response. He then saw the
OL,14,Fdefendant walking away as Hyundai
OL,15,Fstarted to burn."
