OL,7,FMembers of the public who had stopped
OL,8,Fto help reported hearing one of them
OL,9,Fshouting "run, run" as the pair fled
OL,10,Fthe scene, "no doubt realising the
OL,11,Fseverity of what had happened", Ms
OL,12,FPitman told the court.
OL,14,FWhile Mrs Boyack died instantly in the
OL,15,Fcrash, Stephen was taken to Queen's
OL,16,FMedical Centre in Nottingham and his
OL,17,Floved ones were initially told he
OL,18,Fwould survive his injuries, but he
OL,19,Fwent into cardiac arrest and died
OL,20,Fshortly after.
