OL,7,FMs Pitman said: "(Hill) chose not to
OL,8,Fcall for assistance or to attempt to
OL,9,Fspeak to the police or emergency
OL,10,Fservices. He chose to hide from the
OL,11,Fpolice and didn't contact them to
OL,12,Fexplain he was the driver, instead he
OL,13,Fleft the area and went to Sheffield.
OL,15,F"He was effectively on the run and
OL,16,Fpolice went to many addresses of
OL,17,Fpeople who were linked to the
OL,18,Fdefendant in the hope he would hand
OL,19,Fhimself in."
