OL,7,FHill was eventually arrested at his
OL,8,Fmother's address in Sheffield after
OL,9,Fpolice threatened to force entry and
OL,10,Fduring interview, admitted he had been
OL,11,Fthe driver.
OL,13,FHe told officers he "thought he had
OL,14,Fplenty of time" to carry out the
OL,15,Fovertake of the vehicle in front of
OL,16,Fhim but Stephen Boyack's car was
OL,17,F"clearly" closer than he realised.
