OL,7,FHill initially pleaded not guilty to
OL,8,Ftwo counts of causing death by
OL,9,Fdangerous driving but changed his plea
OL,10,Fto guilty on May 10, three weeks
OL,11,Fbefore a trial was due to start.
OL,13,FMitigating, Hill's barrister Simon
OL,14,FEckersley said the defendant was
OL,15,F"genuinely remorseful".
