OL,7,FIn his statement, Mr Boyack said he
OL,8,Fhas "nothing by disgust and contempt"
OL,9,Ffor Hill and his passenger who "stood
OL,10,Fthere and did nothing" as total
OL,11,Fstrangers helped his wife, who worked
OL,12,Fin a library, and his youngest son.
OL,14,FHe said: "I cannot even begin to
OL,15,Fcomprehend what happened that day, I
OL,16,Fget unbearable pains in my chest when
OL,17,FI think about it. Losing my wife and
OL,18,Fson has ruined my life in every sense.
