OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,F"She was a caring, loving wife and a
OL,8,Floving mother. She was everything to
OL,9,Fme.
OL,11,F"But not only have I lost my wife, I
OL,12,Flost my gentle giant son Stephen.
OL,14,F"It has been made worse by the fact he
OL,15,Fwas alive and we were told he was
OL,16,Fgoing to survive. We talked about his
OL,17,Frecovery and what we would do to make
OL,18,Fthat happen. I had to watch losing him
OL,19,Fto his injuries."
