OL,7,FOrdering Hill to serve two-thirds of
OL,8,Fhis 13-year sentence before being
OL,9,Freleased on licence and banning him
OL,10,Ffrom driving for 10 years, Judge
OL,11,FJonathan Straw said Hill had been
OL,12,Fplaying "automotive Russian roulette"
OL,13,Fwhen he overtook the Audi.
OL,15,FHe said: "Angela's 60th birthday would
OL,16,Fhave been on December 12, the same day
OL,17,Fyou appeared at the magistrates' court
OL,18,Ffor the first time charged with her
OL,19,Fand her son's deaths."
